{"tid":523250,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（估國家）擺明搶錢師奶存4500萬台幣卻領不出　銀行：要等82年後","createTime":"2018-01-08T11:01:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-09T11:55:09.000Z","uid":22675,"like":90,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"10fbee94d1454ab13a454429a69403da150e7fa0","tid":523250,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T11:01:00.000Z","msg":"大陸中心／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n哭&hellip;千萬鈔票竟一去不復返！中國大陸一名師奶因貪圖銀行高利息，把1千萬人民幣（約新台幣4500萬）儲蓄存進銀行，未料要領錢時，銀行竟告知要82年後，也就是2099年才能動用，讓女子大傻眼。<br />\n<br />\n千萬,存款,銀行,凍結,儲蓄,利息（圖／翻攝自微博） ID-1205654<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/01/07/1205654-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F01%2F07%2F1205654-XXL.jpg&h=68e71841&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">▲女子的千萬存款就要2099年才可領。（圖／翻攝自微博）</span><br />\n<br />\n據陸媒報導，這名住在浙江寧波的高姓女子，因經商致富，她聽朋友介紹吉林銀行的大連分行年利率很高，在去年5月把1千萬人民幣存進去，未料幾天後想提領鈔票，竟發現帳戶餘額是0元，趕緊打給銀行詢問，對方告知錢已遭到凍結質押，需等2099年才能動用。<br />\n<br />\n更誇張的是，高女並無辦理質押手續，銀行卻回應，是收到分行通知書，她有簽訂「質押擔保委託書」，並核准把這筆錢放款給某家房地產公司，但高女反駁，她根本沒同意，銀行怎能用一張通知書就凍結存款，甚至到最後銀行也拿不出質押證明。<br />\n<br />\n事後高女也向借款的房地產公司查詢，負責人唐姓男子則說，這筆錢是直接跟銀行貸的，並不知道錢從何來，但允諾會還錢，但需給他一些時間籌錢。對此，女子無奈的說，她已經向當地的銀監會管局反映，不排除會通過法律途徑維權。如今該案已過了半年，卻仍沒新進展，至於何時能還錢？銀行方面也未作出正面回應，只強調借款人還清貸款後，存單才能解凍，目前警方已介入調查。"},{"pid":"801935649e6ad59a15e83806b5d24840bd385051","tid":523250,"uid":65406,"like":55,"dislike":3,"score":52,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T11:05:12.000Z","msg":"感謝黨系列。黨既恩賜黎。起天堂留左個位比佢。等佢起上面有錢用"},{"pid":"1b5f5da52fb90fc9191d50f64e008227a635ebc4","tid":523250,"uid":52595,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T11:08:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4fed9c086294e81a254b0451093e54822ef9d79f","tid":523250,"uid":54744,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T11:10:39.000Z","msg":"睇完半澤直樹即刻有音樂出佐黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a0d96841ffa9b55a7b099cc623edfe900790d09","tid":523250,"uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T11:33:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65c87128f37af873f93c891de5ff9ab5fb3c843c","tid":523250,"uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T11:52:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6be93f62960cb7b1dfc7ea7271fe22c61013c307","tid":523250,"uid":52946,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T11:59:02.000Z","msg":"中國既野你地識條春咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eb4bf999cc8b99d08111e03d12796b13d0ccaef","tid":523250,"uid":18912,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T12:04:34.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"00543207272e10dd4182504018934ab907067cb8","tid":523250,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T12:17:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c872315bb329e2d50ac7bb902fc782e15f361e9d","tid":523250,"uid":57023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T12:20:27.000Z","msg":"82年後債主債仔還存在嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c50872049b8d8f7717d1aa1ec6b2f6a9789642f","tid":523250,"uid":28913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T22:59:07.000Z","msg":"中國既銀行古惑到好似商家佬咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ced50b8f664ae6fc160729baf443f890ce362c0d","tid":523250,"uid":52595,"like":33,"dislike":1,"score":32,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T23:03:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2a4a8d71af66278ea637331d6f352a12cb04b208","tid":523250,"uid":6799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ced50b8f664ae6fc160729baf443f890ce362c0d","tid":523250,"uid":52595,"like":33,"dislike":1,"score":32,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T23:03:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"